@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>This is a demonstration application for Azure SRE Agent testing. No real personal data is collected or stored beyond the demo user accounts created for testing purposes.</p>

<h3>Data Collected</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>User Accounts</strong> - Username, email, and hashed passwords stored in Azure SQL Database</li>
    <li><strong>Session Data</strong> - Login timestamps stored in session cookies</li>
    <li><strong>Application Telemetry</strong> - Performance metrics and logs sent to Application Insights</li>
</ul>

<h3>Purpose</h3>
<p>All data in this application exists solely for the purpose of demonstrating Azure SRE Agent capabilities including monitoring, alerting, and incident response.</p>
